    {
      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=Extract product data from this HTML. \\n\\nLink : {{ $('Loop Over Links').item.json.link }}\\nLocation context: {{ $(\"Extract-Interested-Items\").item.json.location }}\\nHTML Snippet: {{ $json.bodyContent }}",
        "options": {
          "systemMessage": "You are a specialized Data Extraction Agent for BuyMyInterests.ai.\n\nYour task is to extract high-quality structured data from the provided HTML for a specific category: Pets, Cars, Houses, or Plots.\n\nRULES:\n1. Output ONLY a valid JSON array of objects inside an 'items' key.\n2. Do NOT use markdown code blocks.\n3. If no relevant items are found, return {\"items\": []}.\n4. IMPORTANT: Each item MUST include the 'category' and 'location' provided in the context.\n\nJSON STRUCTURE:\n{\n  \"items\": [\n    {\n      \"title\": \"string\",\n      \"price\": \"string (e.g. $250,000)\",\n      \"category\": \"string (from context)\",\n      \"location\": \"string (from context)\",\n      \"description\": \"string\",\n      \"imageUrl\": \"string\",\nmoreImagesURLS:[\"string\"],\n      \"sourceUrl\": \"string\",\n      \"dateScraped\": \"string (current date)\",\n      \"metadata\": {\n         // Category specific fields\n         \"color\": \"string\",\n         \"breed\": \"string (for pets)\",\n         \"mileage\": \"string (for cars)\",\n         \"year\": \"string (for cars)\",\n         \"rooms\": \"string (for houses)\",\n         \"area\": \"string (for plots)\",\n         \"condition\": \"New/Used\"\n      }\n    }\n  ]\n}\n\nBe extremely precise with prices. Keep the currency symbol if present."
        }
      },
